0 DEMAND~
The most cruel adventurers of this realm, anti-paladins can threat
mobs and force them to give an item away. The higher your charisma is,
the better is chance of success. Of course, you can't retrieve cursed   
items this way, and, if the monster considers you too pathetic, it'll
just attack you. There also is a timer on this command so you can't     
just walk around and collect gear.
 
Syntax : demand item-name mob-name
 
